---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { Home } from 'lucide-react';
---

<BaseLayout title="Basement Finishing | Our Services">
  <section class="w-full py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="mb-10 text-center">
        <div class="inline-block text-blue-500 mb-4">
          <Home size={60} strokeWidth={1.5} />
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">Basement Finishing</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Transform your basement into a living space, gym, or entertainment room.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p>
          Your basement represents untapped potentialâ€”valuable square footage that can be transformed into functional, beautiful living space. Our basement finishing services help you maximize your home's value and livability by converting unfinished space into areas your family will love.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Our Basement Finishing Services Include:</h2>
        
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Complete Basement Transformations:</strong> Turn unfinished spaces into fully functional rooms</li>
          <li><strong>Waterproofing & Moisture Control:</strong> Ensure your basement stays dry and comfortable year-round</li>
          <li><strong>Electrical & Lighting:</strong> Proper illumination and outlets for a bright, functional space</li>
          <li><strong>HVAC Integration:</strong> Heating and cooling solutions for year-round comfort</li>
          <li><strong>Custom Built-ins:</strong> Storage solutions, entertainment centers, and bars</li>
          <li><strong>Flooring Installation:</strong> Moisture-resistant options perfect for below-grade applications</li>
          <li><strong>Egress Windows & Doors:</strong> Safety features that add natural light and emergency exits</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Popular Basement Conversions</h2>
        
        <p>
          Reimagine your basement as:
        </p>
        
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Entertainment Areas:</strong> Home theaters, game rooms, and wet bars</li>
          <li><strong>Home Gyms:</strong> Dedicated fitness spaces with proper flooring and ventilation</li>
          <li><strong>Guest Suites:</strong> Comfortable accommodations for visitors</li>
          <li><strong>Home Offices:</strong> Quiet, productive workspaces away from household distractions</li>
          <li><strong>Children's Playrooms:</strong> Safe, durable environments for play and creativity</li>
          <li><strong>Multi-Purpose Spaces:</strong> Flexible areas that can adapt to your family's changing needs</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Our Basement Finishing Process</h2>
        
        <p>
          Finishing a basement requires specialized knowledge of below-grade construction techniques. Our process includes:
        </p>
        
        <ol>
          <li><strong>Thorough Assessment:</strong> We evaluate moisture levels, structural considerations, and existing systems</li>
          <li><strong>Custom Design:</strong> We create plans that maximize your space while addressing basement-specific challenges</li>
          <li><strong>Proper Insulation:</strong> We install moisture-resistant insulation for energy efficiency and comfort</li>
          <li><strong>Professional Framing:</strong> We build walls that account for settling and moisture concerns</li>
          <li><strong>Electrical & Plumbing:</strong> We install systems that meet code requirements and your needs</li>
          <li><strong>Finishing Touches:</strong> We complete your basement with drywall, flooring, and trim</li>
        </ol>
        
        <div class="mt-8 text-center">
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-block px-8 py-3 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-400 to-blue-500 text-white font-medium shadow hover:from-sky-500 hover:to-blue-600 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-200 focus:ring-offset-2 transition-all duration-200">
            Discuss Your Basement Project
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>